Find out what books, reports, articles, and interviews have already been published 
on your topic of interest. Look for new angles and fresh ways to approach familiar 
subjects, and keep a lookout for specialized sub-topics that haven't already been 
extensively covered.

Once you've hired your writer, be prepared to spend some time with them, 
educating them about your topic and your goals. Until your writer understands 
"the big picture," they're going to have a difficult time writing an info product that 
truly meets your objectives.

For members of the SGI,\rKosen Rufu means the\rceaseless effort to enhance\rthe value of human dignity,\rto awaken all people to a\rsense of their limitless\rworth and potential. It is for\rthis reason that efforts in\rthe fields of peace,\rhumanitarian aid,\reducational and cultural\rexchange are all seen as\rvital aspects of the\rmovement for Kosen Rufu.\r\'Kosen Rufu does not mean\rthe end point or terminus of\ra flow, but it is the flow\ritself, the very pulse of\rliving Buddhism within\rsociety.\' (Daisaku Ikeda)

In Lifetime after Lifetime we create\rkarma on three levels: through the\rCAUSES of thoughts, words and deeds\rthat instantaneously store anticipated\rEFFECTS deep within our lives. Deeds\rof course have a greater impact than\rmere words. Likewise, when we\rverbalise our ideas, this creates\rdeeper karma than merely thinking\rthem. However, since both words and\rdeeds originate in thoughts, the\rcontents of our hearts--our\rthoughts--are also of crucial\rimportance.

Karma can be thought of as our core\rpersonality, the profound tendencies that have\rbeen impressed into the deepest levels of our\rlives. The deepest cycles of cause and effect\rextend beyond the present existence; they\rshape the manner in which we start this\rlife--our particular circumstances from the\rmoment of birth--and will continue beyond our\rdeaths. The purpose of Buddhist practice is to\rtransform our basic life tendency in order to\rrealise our total human potential in this\rlifetime and beyond.

\'If you want to understand the causes\rthat existed in the past, look at the\rresults as they are manifested in the\rpresent. And if you want to\runderstand what results will be\rmanifested in the future, look at the\rcauses that exist in the present.\'\r(WND No.30, p279)

Karma is thus, like everything, in constant\rflux. We create our own present and\rfuture by the choices we make in each\rmoment. Understood in this light, the\rteaching of karma does not encourage\rresignation, but empowers us to become\rthe protagonists in the unfolding drama of\rour lives.
3 GREAT SECRET\rLAWS (hidden in\rthe Lotus Sutra)\r(WND No.35\rp320)

The Gohonzon is the object of devotion in\rNichiren Buddhism. In Japanese, \'go\' means\rworthy of honour and \'honzon\' means object\rof fundamental respect. Nichiren defined the\runiversal law permeating life and the universe\ras Nam-Myoho-Renge-Kyo and embodied it in\rthe form of a mandala. In the Gohonzon, a\rscroll on which are inscribed Chinese and\rSanskrit characters, Nichiren symbolically\rdepicted the life state of Buddhahood, which\rall people possess. The Gohonzon, together\rwith a practitioner\'s faith and chanting of\rNam-Myoho-Renge-Kyo, acts as a stimulus to\ractivate the life-condition of Buddhahood\rinnate in one\'s life. As such the Gohonzon\rfunctions as External Cause for the\rmanifestation of the Life State of\rBuddhahood.

ONENESS of SELF &\rENVIRONMENT\r      (Esho Funi)\r    Life and its\rEnvironment are 2\rIndependent\rPhenomena but 1 in\rtheir Fundamental\rEssence. (\'2 but not\r2 and not 2 but 2\')\r(WND No.79, p647)

THE BENEVOLENCE AND POWER OF THE GOHONZON  \'The\rbenevolence and power of the Gohonzon are boundless and\rlimitless and the work is immeasurable and unfathomable.\rTherefore, if you take faith in this Gohonzon and chant\rNam-Myoho-Renge-Kyo, even for a while, no prayer will go\runanswered, no sin will remain un-forgiven, all good fortune will be\rbestowed, and all righteousness will be proven.\' (Nichikan Shonin)
ONENESS OF BODY & MIND\rIntegration of the Spiritual\r& Physical are aspects of\revery single Life

‘If you wish to free yourself from the sufferings of\rbirth and death you have endured since time without\rbeginning and to attain without fail unsurpassed\renlightenment in this lifetime, you must perceive the\rmystic truth that is originally inherent in all living\rbeings. This truth is Myoho-Renge-Kyo. Chanting\rMyoho-Renge-Kyo will therefore enable you to grasp\rthe mystic truth innate in all life. The Lotus Sutra is\rthe king of sutras, true and correct in both word and\rprinciple. Its words are the ultimate reality, and this\rreality is the Mystic Law (Myoho). It is called the\rMystic Law because it reveals the principle of the\rmutually inclusive relationship of a single moment of\rlife and all phenomena. That is why this sutra is the\rwisdom of all Buddhas. Life at each moment\rencompasses the body and mind and the self and\renvironment of all sentient beings in the Ten Worlds\ras well as all insentient beings in the three thousand\rrealms, including plants, sky, earth, and even the\rminutest particles of dust. Life at each moment\rpermeates the entire realm of phenomena and is\rrevealed in all phenomena.’ The Writings of Nichiren\rDaishonin (WND No.1, P 3)

PERSEVERANCE \'The journey from Kamakura to\rKyoto takes twelve days. If you travel for eleven\rbut stop with only one day remaining, how can you\radmire the moon over the capital?\' (WND No.145,\rp1026)

Having studied widely among all\rthe Buddhist sutras, Nichiren\rDaishonin had concluded that\rthe Lotus Sutra contains the\rultimate truth of Buddhism: that\reveryone without exception has\rthe potential to attain\rBuddhahood. The title\r(Daimoku) of the Lotus Sutra in\rits Japanese translation is\rMyoho-Renge-Kyo. But to\rNichiren, Myoho-Renge-Kyo was\rfar more than the title of a\rBuddhist text, it was the\rexpression, in words, of the Law\rof life which all Buddhist\rteachings in one way or another\rseek to clarify.

THE HERITAGE OF THE ULTIMATE\rLAW OF LIFE   \'Be resolved to\rsummon forth the great power of\rfaith, and chant Nam-Myoho-Renge-Kyo\rwith the prayer that\ryour faith will be steadfast and\rcorrect at the moment of death.\rNever seek any other way to\rinherit the ultimate Law of life and\rdeath, and manifest it in your life.\'\r(WND No.29, p218)

SGI is a Buddhist Society for the Creation of Value\rthrough \'Human Revolution\'. This is the idea that the\rself-motivated inner change of a single individual\rpositively affects the larger web of life and results in the\rrejuvenation of society and the environment.
SGI is a truly world-wide movement for\rpeace, education and culture,\rfundamentally based on the life-affirming\rBuddhist philosophy of Nichiren\rDaishonin.

A reformist educator, author and philosopher Tsunesaburo\rMakiguchi & his colleague Josei Toda founded the Soka\rKyoiku Gakkai (the forerunner of the Soka Gakkai).\rDaisaku Ikeda is the current (3rd) President of SGI.

fólk greinir þrjá grunnliti:  gult,\rblátt og rautt
gult er grunnlitur frekar en blanda af rauðu og blágrænu ljósi. \n \n
Neikvæðar myndleifar (color afterimages) benda\rtil að rautt og grænt eru uppbótarlitir\r(complementary colors) eins og blátt og    gult.\r
Hver tegund hefur ólíkt opsin sem næmt er\rfyrir tiltekinni bylgjulengd (blue, red, green),\rsem styður þrílitakenninguna

is a deferred annuity contract between an\rindividual contract owner (policyowner) and a\rlife insurance company.
The investment returns and\rbenefits from an IVIC are not\rguaranteed.
The value of the IVIC is tied to the\rvalue of the segregated fund portfolio\rheld under the IVIC.
The date on which an\rinvestor makes his or her\rfirst deposit.

The date on which a deposit maturity benefit is applicable. It is\rgenerally a date 10 years from the contract date or, in the case\rof subsequent deposits, from a specific policy year date. If the\rIVIC features a reset option, and the client chooses to reset the\rmaturity, the new maturity date is 10 years from the reset date.

The date upon which the investments held under a\rsegregated funds deferred annuity policy are valued for\rpurposes of the death benefit (the date of death of the life\rinsured) and maturity (the original or reset maturity date)\rguarantees.
However, IVICs also have characteristics\rthat are different from standard life\rinsurance contracts:
IVIC contract owners do not get a 10-day\rfree look before deciding whether to keep\rthe policy.

IVICs do not contain a suicide exclusion clause.\rConsequently, death benefit guarantees are paid\reven if the cause of death is suicide and even if\rdeath occurs within the first two years of the contract.
Under an IVIC, there is generally no requirement\rfor the contract owner to submit medical\rinformation or to undergo a medical examination.\r

A maturity guarantee is a guarantee from the insurance\rcompany stating that on the maturity date, provided the\rinvestment has been held for 10 years, the investor is entitled\rto receive the higher of:
statutory minimum guarantee of 75% of\rthe principal investment in the segregated\rfund
The insurance company also guarantees to pay a\rdeath benefit to the policy beneficiary if the\rannuitant dies before the maturity date. Generally,\rthe death benefit is calculated as the higher of:
the market value of the\rsegregated fund units held under\rthe contract
depending on the specific policy,\r75% or 100% of the principal\rinvestment
Insurance legislation requires the death\rbenefit to be at least 75% of the\rpayments to the contract.
Age restrictions on the\rdeath benefit guarantee

Paragone tra ecosistema delle tecnologie\rdella comunicazione e ecosistema\rnaturale.
Nel mondo della comunicazione l\'arrivo di nuove tecnologie non implica\rla morte delle precedenti, ma semmai una loro riorganizzazione.
Le specie comunicative non muoiono quasi\rmai: entrano in nicchie e nel\rcollezionismo.

Paragone con i Piranha, che, introdotti in un lago (come per\resempio il Lago Maggiore), al contrario delle aspettative, non\rfarebbero scomparire completamente gli Agoni, ma li\rridurrebbero di numero. I superstiti a quel punto si\rriorganizzerebbero.
nuove tecnologie coesistono e\rcoevolvono con le precedenti.
i nuovi media non nascono\rspontaneamente, ma emergono\rgradualmente dalla metamorfosi di media più\rvecchi.
i nuovi media portano con sè, nella\rloro evoluzione, qualcosa dei\rprecedenti.
evoluzione per la sopravvivenza obbligata da\run contesto in continuo cambiamento, pena\rla morte del prodotto stesso (es: Swissinfo).

trasformazioni spinte che derivano dal contesto. Per esempio, il fax non è completamente\rsparito nonostante l’avvento delle e-mail. Esiste sempre e comunque il numero di fax nei\rbiglietti da visita di un’attività lavorativa, sia per questioni legislative che per questioni di tipo\reconomico.
perchè una tecnologia si integri pienamente\rdeve passare del tempo, e perchè questa si\rstabilizzi, deve prendere i ritmi delle azioni\rumane.

玄玄海围棋。\n60天，培养儿童注意力，提高学习能力！

亚里士多德4段论：
1绪论 为什么围棋能帮你的小孩提高注意力？
2问题 儿童注意力水平决定其学习能力，注意力不能有效集中则学习能力一定会受到影响。
3对策 围棋作为一种高级智力活动，是改善儿童注意力，提高学习能力的最佳盘上游戏。
4展望 让孩子学习围棋，全面促进孩子的注意力、思维力、竞争力！
任课教师，秦老师，业余三段棋手，长期从事围棋的教育价值和少儿教育理论的学习和实践，\n服膺小林宗作（《窗边的小豆豆》）、雷夫·艾斯奎（《第56号教室的奇迹》）的教育理念，\n致力于树立少儿围棋学习的新模式，即：快乐围棋、人文围棋、教育的围棋。

儿童注意力集中程度比成年人低，在学习中表现为：
上课不注意听讲，不能全面掌握学习内容；
又由于自控能力差，上课多动，不能坚持、深入，缺乏耐心，
做作业时粗心大意、马虎潦草、边做边玩，考试时不认真答卷，
常有看错题、漏题的现象，因而严重地影响学习成绩。

科研人员发现，注意相关认知电位可以反映大脑对注意到的信息的内在处理能力，
该指标与学习能力和智商密切相关。在注意相关认知电位指标上，
智商高、学习能力较强学生与学习能力较低的学生有明显的差别。
注意力集中水平越高，学生的学习能力就越强。反之亦然。
在游戏中启迪智慧，于棋道中培养人格。\n（从游戏中开启智慧，于棋道中人格养成）
